{"tid":2210061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【錄埋出嚟Diu多次】既然黃絲咁鐘意互屌 就等我屌哂你地所有人 2","createTime":"2020-09-20T06:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T14:26:59.000Z","uid":82955,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6196c4bcc3a63ecc030ab0f086ed2b20b89439","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"之前見到有位Ching Post咗段文字Diu到大家飛起 <br />\n<blockquote>既然黃絲咁鐘意互屌,就等我屌哂你地所有人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2205098\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2205098</a></blockquote><br />\n覺得都幾有道理同幾有能量拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我加加減減內容再加入咗啲自己諗法 <br />\n仲走去錄埋出嚟 希望大家聽到又會感受深啲<br />\n唔鐘意聽我把聲嘅話 <span class=\"gold\"><strong>你都要直飛片尾呀 片尾你會鐘意的</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4jKKcbL1pk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB4jKKcbL1pk&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=28ec2629\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4jKKcbL1pk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFUCQrDlg7N/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFUCQrDlg7N%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=37d07f6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFUCQrDlg7N%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&h=04c82bc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFUCQrDlg7N/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</a><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n雖然同連登文化唔是咁match<br />\n但都想講兩句提提大家<br />\n<strong><span class=\"pink\">「世界真的不是那麼美好 所以你必然要更努力保守你心 掙扎 愛你」</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcaa6a2ce36fa70c9832e8319b2cb25b4a5c8e8","tid":2210061,"uid":281105,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾，不推文回，負皮"},{"pid":"c11fdfeb2d692ec2c269b2f387fd9bd6b8aa7848","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得:<br />\n「齊上齊學」<br />\n「光復自己」<br />\n「Be Humble」<br />\n「革自己的命」<br />\n<br />\n憤恨中請你不要被黑暗吞噬<br />\n我知咁樣同連登仔 (我都係) 講好唔尋常呀<br />\n但我想講 你地就係黑暗中嘅果一點光<br />\n你地都鼓勵咗好多人好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係真架<br />\n掙扎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9b3ef67031b6de612709765970f2cf3a4d03dc","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"推 齊上齊學"},{"pid":"391451d3d71aec19ac64610b560c2dc252d37c78","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"推 光復自己"},{"pid":"126bf5376978c8c9fb9586d2d98b7237434bb488","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"推 BE HUMBLE"},{"pid":"af5b33c45d3e349f6987213fda0fa07ee548980b","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"推 革自己的命"},{"pid":"2f65acb6d6be0b7c9110105537a60d4dc858a8bc","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"推 齊上齊學"},{"pid":"14a0d93309a390b768ce096e4e03c46031d5793a","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"推 光復自己"},{"pid":"f1acd0c6cf00dd57238e658d6b42c0e4b3d36e9c","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"推 BE HUMBLE"},{"pid":"d2af17e1d2ad92c9394bca282a8744743013102a","tid":2210061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,